  "calendar": [],
  "general_provisions": "This bill moves the election of a local school board member to coincide with the municipal election dates in an odd-numbered year.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>moves a primary election for a local school board office to the date of a municipal primary election;<hr><ltbullet>moves a general election for a local school board office to the date of a municipal general election;<hr><ltbullet>modifies the declaration of candidacy period for a local school board office;<hr><ltbullet>extends the term of office of certain local school board members to effectuate the transition from elections held in even-numbered years to elections held in odd-numbered years; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming amendments. ",
